node.text: Damn the katsu looks so crispy!

[Chef Avenue] - The Bundle Meals for 2 pax promo at &16 is very worth it. I have the combo B set which consists of
🍱🍱🍱
- Japanese Curry Pork Katsu Rice
- Japanese Curry Fish Katsu Rice
- Tori Karaage, Kakiage, Spam
- Miso Soup
.
I also had the Beef Garlic Fried Rice and Spicy Double Salmon Roll.
.

Customers can call 8777 3163 to make their orders. delivery charges are as follows: 
Min $35 spending: $6
> $60 spending: Free delivery islandwide
What camera did you use for this picture??
Thank you and hope u enjoyed the meal :)
